Fleshgrinder is zero taunt other than the DPS as the proc is a Direct Damage and most mobs ignore these types of procs.<br>
Fleshgrinder makes a great offhand.<br>
The wavecrasher is very little taunt from my experience using one, especially if you are planning to play in PoP zones where it is required to have a slower to really be effective in exp grinding. Without a slower the downtime is too much because your healers have to heal to much.<br>
Wavecrasher proc will never land if you have a slower in your group and doesnt generate any taunt. Wavecrasher is the most over-rated weapon I have ever used and I dumped it as fast as I could when I got one. Others may have a differing opinion, but I think you are better off using a Frostbringer over a wavecrasher and the frosty is way cheaper too.<br>
<br>
Naralli Ironsmith<br>
